data.description: Stunning estate with all the upgrades and finishes that you are accustomed to in a home like this! Neutral paint throughout with tasteful touches everywhere you turn.  Walk in and stand impressed seeing the grand foyer, formal dining room, and spacious office all welcoming you into the home.  The grand fireplace and spacious living room flow into the kitchen and eating area so nicely.   An open plan without feeling exposed! The gorgeous renovated kitchen has all-new appliances and a layout any chef will appreciate.  All the bedrooms are spacious and accommodating for any size of furniture and are arranged in a way to give everyone space of their own.  The master is stunning with a renovated bathroom that includes a whirlpool tub. There is something new to fall in love with in every room! Gorgeous grounds lead out to an in-ground private pool with entertaining areas.  This home has it all plus is so close to everything.  There is nothing to want or desire from this home or the location - it is the total package!
